flowchart TD

%% User Layer
User[Employee UI / Slack / Teams Bot]
Auth[AWS Cognito / IAM Identity Center]
API[Amazon API Gateway]

User --> Auth --> API

%% Orchestration
API --> Orchestrator[LangGraph / Step Functions]

%% Async Layer
Orchestrator <--> Queue[Amazon SQS / EventBridge]

%% Agents
Orchestrator --> Router[Router Agent]
Router --> Agents[Retriever / Answer / Critic / Security Agents]

%% Guardrails
Agents --> Guardrails[Guardrails Layer (PII / Prompt Defense / Output Validation)]

%% MCP Layer
Guardrails --> MCP[MCP Server (ECS / Lambda)]

MCP --> Registry[Tool Registry]
MCP --> RBAC[IAM + RBAC Policies]
MCP --> Policy[Policy Engine]
MCP --> Validator[Schema Validator]
MCP --> MCPLogs[Audit Logger]

%% LLM Layer
MCP --> LLMGateway[LLM Gateway]
LLMGateway --> Bedrock[Amazon Bedrock]

%% Enterprise Systems
MCP --> Systems[SAP / ServiceNow / HRMS APIs]

%% Knowledge Layer
Agents --> HRDB[(HR Vector DB - OpenSearch)]
Agents --> ITDB[(IT Vector DB - OpenSearch)]
Agents --> FINDB[(Finance Vector DB - OpenSearch)]

%% Memory + Cache
Agents --> Cache[(ElastiCache Redis)]
Agents --> Memory[(Conversation Memory Store)]

%% Storage
Agents --> S3[(Amazon S3)]

%% Human in Loop
Agents --> HITL[Human Review UI]
HITL --> Orchestrator

%% Monitoring
Agents --> Logs[CloudWatch Logs]
MCPLogs --> Logs
Logs --> Monitor[CloudWatch + X-Ray + CloudTrail]